      <div class="row">
        <div  class="col-8">
            <p class="lead">
                AppStreams provide a definition of common Application Services and Data Models that are used in Cities across the world.
            </p>
            <p>
                The goal is to collaborarively create sets of reusable definitions that will improve integration, interoperability and allow
                people developing services for Citizens and Business to be able to focus on the problem rather than the underlying platform details.
            </p>
            <h4>Services and Models</h4>
            <div>
                <p>
                    We have an increasing collection of common City Services that, where possible, use and integrate existing work around the world.
                </p>
